SUMMARY:IP Year End & Retirement Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Mark your Calendars for a very special CIPR and IPA Year End 
 Celebration! This year not only will we gather together to celebrate anot
 her fantastic year but we will also take time to honor two special people
  who are retiring at the end of the academic year: Professor Don Knebel a
 nd Professor Norm Hedges  Maurer faculty\, students\, and alumni are warm
 ly invited to attend.  RSVP by noon on April 15th.&#160\;
