 ating class for the LSSSE! (Winning class to be announced when the LSSSE 
 closes in April!)  During the lunch hour on Tuesday\, April 21\, come by 
 starting at 12pm to get some lunch\, enjoy the (hopefully) nice weather o
 n the ground floor patio\, and celebrate the near-end of this academic ye
 ar!&#160\;
