SUMMARY:Finals Fuel: Movie Night Study Sesh
DESCRIPTION:Take a break from outlining and recharge with a low-stress st
 udy session with outlines disguised as movie night. We'll be watching Fin
 ding Nemo and Ratatouille while getting some light studying in before fin
 als. Come hang out\, review notes\, or just relax for a bitŌĆöyou can mak
 e it as productive (or not) as you need.We'll have plenty of movie-themed
  snacks to keep you going\, including Goldfish (GF and regular)\, Swedish
  Fish\, Rice Krispie Treats\, popcorn\, cookies (GF and regular)\, plus d
 rinks and some fruit.Whether you stay the whole time or just swing by bet
 ween study blocks\, it's a good chance to reset and get a little finals m
 otivation in.&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><span style="font-family: 'Arial'\,sans-s
 erif\; color: black\;">Take a break from outlining and recharge with a lo
 w-stress study session with outlines disguised as movie night. We'll be w
 atching Finding Nemo and Ratatouille while getting some light studying in
  before finals. Come hang out\, review notes\, or just relax for a bitŌĆö
 you can make it as productive (or not) as you need.</span></p><p><span st
 yle="font-family: 'Arial'\,sans-serif\; color: black\;">We'll have plenty
  of movie-themed snacks to keep you going\, including Goldfish (GF and re
 gular)\, Swedish Fish\, Rice Krispie Treats\, popcorn\, cookies (GF and r
 egular)\, plus drinks and some fruit.</span></p><p><span style="font-fami
 ly: 'Arial'\,sans-serif\; color: black\;">Whether you stay the whole time
  or just swing by between study blocks\, it's a good chance to reset and 
 get a little finals motivation in.&#160\;</span></p>
